      while also wholesaling properties. Through those JVs and through learning
      the art of wholesaling, I started making some serious money as I was all
      in on real estate.

      <br />
      <br />

      At the same time, I was reading a lot of books on self development, like
      Bob Proctor's, Change Your Paradigm Change Your Life, or The Science of
      Getting Rich by Wallace D. Wattles, The Power of Awarness and the Wealth
