      Phillipines, etc. Those two years were essential for the awakening that we
      are creators of our reality. The reason Imention this is that the universe
      has a way of putting all your experiences together in the now and all the
      experiences that I have had and that you too have had and are having that
      point to the wisdom that we are powerful and have the ability to create
      our lives.

      <br />
      <br />

