      investors that were struggling with one aspect or another ofeal estate
      investing. So instead of not doing anything and continue to see them
      struggle, I decided that I could make a difference and help them in their
      real estate journey. I coach not because of the money, I coach because I
      am passionate about seeing others succeed. I enjoy seeing my students's or
      mentee's growth and see them achieve goals they never thought were
      possible.

      <br />
      <br />

      I have all the tools, wisdom, knowledge, and resources to help you achieve
      amazing things in your real estate business and life! This year, my goal
